captions.text: Oh! Oh! Jingeo
Oh! Oh! Oh! Jingeo!
Don't make fun of me
Don't laugh!
I'm a squid, good for health and tasty!
People call me Ojingeo (squid)
When people stand next to me, they call me Ojingeo
I don't think I'm ugly
If I'm really Ojingeo,
then are you an octopus? or flatfish?
a flounder?
What makes you think you're better than me?
They make fun of me saying "Hey, Ojingeo" when I arrive
They make fun of me saying "Bye, Ojingeo" when I leave

When I get some fresh air, they make fun of me,
calling me I'm a half-dried squid
Whatever I do, they call me Ojingeo
Everyone thinks they're the best
You don't have to make it fit under the rules
It's your life, like a lego blocks
Parboiled squid, fried squid, squid sausage

Choose whatever you want
Because I'm a squid
When my feelings are hurt, you will get hurt too
When I'm sick, you'll get sick too
When you're hurt, my heart will get hurt too
Leave me alone, please go!
Girls call her Doenjang-nyuh (gold digger)
They call her gold digger because she was just holding something
I don't think she is
If she is really Doenjang-nyuh,
then are you a cheese girl? margarine girl?
Balsamic girl?
What makes you think you're better than her?

They make fun of her, calling her Doenjang-nyuh
when she buys a new bag,
when she drinks a cup of coffee

They make fun of her, calling her Doenjang-nyuh
when she eats real Doenjang (Soy bean paste)
You don't have to make it fit under the rules
It's your life, like a lego blocks
Stew, rice wrapped in greens, pancakes, soup
Choose whatever you want
Because she's Doenjang-nyuh
When my feelings are hurt, you will get hurt too
When I'm sick, you'll get sick too
When you're hurt, my heart will get hurt too
Leave me alone, please go!
It's good, soy bean paste is good
Some people really need squids
It's good, soy bean paste is good
Squids can be a nice meal for someone
Try it, try it, speak after you try it
Try it, try it, in what ways are you better than me?
When my feelings are hurt, you will get hurt too
When I'm sick, you'll get sick too
When you're hurt, my heart will get hurt too
Leave me alone, please go!
Ojingeo Ojingeo Ojingeo Ojingeo
Doenjang Doenjang Doenjang
I love it, we love it
